{"tid":781841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《魔獸世界》驚見小熊維尼與他的快樂夥伴...","createTime":"2018-08-16T08:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T05:49:05.000Z","uid":184679,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"17146d26399b7ec9112b07d00f5363f39097cb53","tid":781841,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T08:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php1RADEZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php1RADEZ.jpg&h=65cfb2c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官方在魔獸世界中設計小熊維尼彩蛋。（圖片取自Reddit）<br />\n<br />\n暴雪娛樂線上遊戲《魔獸世界》在中國擁有廣大玩家支持，但最近有外國網友發現，官方在遊戲內設計了一個彩蛋，讓一隻熊、騾子、老虎、小豬等動物，與一名獵人「羅賓」坐在一起，無疑是在致敬迪士尼經典動畫《小熊維尼》，這也讓外國網友笑說，「我所看到的就只有中國國家主席」。<br />\n<br />\n美國論壇「Reddit」有網友貼出一張遊戲照，可看見一隻「蜜熊」與老虎、小豬和憂鬱的騾子坐在一起，身後還有好幾罐蜂蜜，在他們對面的則是「獵人羅賓」，明顯就是在致敬《小熊維尼》。網友留言表示，「我所看到的就只有中國國家主席」、「無法想像這個版本能在中國存活多久」、「他越禁止被拿來比較，大家的印象只會越深刻」、「我怎沒看到歐巴馬對於他被形容是跳跳虎感到生氣」、「遊戲在中國被禁了」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2520889\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2520889&d=hmXJPBa3pcuiSTTUdUP3QP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=37c9cd0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2520889&h=2317f675\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2520889</a>"},{"pid":"a88066a0afc1d08a4a13c0b4cb294199fa338fcb","tid":781841,"uid":18772,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T10:15:56.000Z","msg":"我諗迪迪尼同美國可能唔知唔相信自己套卡通永久禁止出現係大陸"},{"pid":"ff44e1daa19a562d2eb6ef0b22315944d4d065e8","tid":781841,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T10:17:17.000Z","msg":"開個部落ac隊冧佢"},{"pid":"3cb390368e92c7001c94bf276e146083f5e8fd26","tid":781841,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:21:57.000Z","msg":"大陸版唔知重有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a27f694185737e70838c897c77daf67f6022df","tid":781841,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:22:30.000Z","msg":"打個時笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd2db9c496d8e7629c4a1782526ffe7cb9221b5","tid":781841,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:49:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}